Exmatrikulator Grunt
====================

Node Installation
-----------------

1. Download source of latest NodeJS version from https://nodejs.org/
2. Extract files, execute configure script, then compile it with make and
   finally use make install


Install grunt client
--------------------

Open terminal and execute:
npm install -g grunt-cli
(Can be possible that it's necessary to use sudo.)


Install dependencies
--------------------

Open path exmatrikaltor-code/src/main/gui in terminal and execute:
npm install
Then same command in folder exmatrikaltor-code/src/main/gui/vendors/bootstrap


Build Stylesheets and Javascript
--------------------------------

Open path exmatrikaltor-code/src/main/gui in terminal and execute:
grunt build --force